    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the candles are all burned down to nothing... and so am i. he's gone, and the silence in this house is heavier than the stone in the graveyard. it feels so much more poetic to just... stop. to let the darkness take me rather than face another dawn without him. wouldn't it be more beautiful if i just faded away into the night?",
